				\begin{document}$$ {\rm hist} \left[ x \right] = \frac{{{\rm Num} \left[ x \right]}}{{{\rm TotalNum} }} $$\end{document}where x (0 ≤ x ≤ 255) is gradation, Num[x] is the number of pixels for the gradation x in the color bar, and TotalNum is the total number of pixels of the color bar.
